verbose_text: CRF (100 nM), which had minimal effect on I K (Ca) by itself (XREF_FIG), significantly augmented the small I K (Ca) facilitation produced by a low concentration (0.5 muM) of phenylephrine (XREF_FIG), while there was no significant CRF effect on I K (Ca) facilitation caused by 1 muM phenylephrine (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
